be added}}\n\\newcommand{\\notethat}[1]{\\textcolor{red}{#1}}\n\
\\newcommand{\\impliesthat}{$\\implies$}\n\n% complex coordinates\n\
\\newcommand{\\hb}{\\bar{h}}\n\\newcommand{\\wbar}{\\bar{w}}\n\
